Nicole Forester https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicole_Forester 0 Nicole Forester (born November 19, 1972) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as "Maggie Zajac" on the Starz original series Boss and as "Cassie Layne Winslow" on Guiding Light. She currently appears as "Christie" on NBC's Chicago Fire.
